@vars f=__dirname,m=REFERENCES_DIR,l=REMOTE_SOURCES,u=cache,d=CACHE_TTL
fetchReference(name)→join,cache.get,Date.now,AbortSignal.timeout,fetch,response.text|fetch remote markdown reference with caching and local fallback
listAvailable()→Object.keys,existsSync,readdirSync,f.endsWith,basename,names.add|list available framework references from cache and local dir
export getFrameworkReference(options=)→listAvailable,available.includes,fetchReference,content.split,detectProjectRuleSets,matchedRefs.includes|get full reference docs for a framework or auto-detect
PATTERNS: in-memory caching with TTL|fetch with AbortSignal timeout
EDGE_CASES: gracefully handles fetch timeouts and write failures